00:52:43,760 --> 00:52:44,620
Oke.

451
00:52:46,080 --> 00:52:47,040
Aku Ibu yang baik.

452
00:52:50,930 --> 00:52:52,040
Kau bilang padaku baik-baik saja.

453
00:52:59,450 --> 00:53:00,540
Itu tidak sulit.

454
00:53:04,440 --> 00:53:05,400
Hei...

455
00:53:19,980 --> 00:53:21,380
Bu?

456
00:53:25,200 --> 00:53:27,000
Halo, kawan? Dia di sana, pergilah.

